11 An Act relating to human trafficking; amending 21
O.S. 2021, Section 13.1, as last amended by Section
12 1, Chapter 352, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 13.1), which relates to required service of
13 prison sentences; specifying type of offense that
requires mandatory service of sentence; amending 21
14 O.S. 2021, Section 749, as last amended by Section
20, Chapter 486, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
15 Section 748), which relates to human trafficking;
modifying elements of crime to include certain
16 victims; providing separate penalty provisions;
amending 57 O.S. 2021, Section 138, as last amended
17 by Section 1, Chapter 132, O.S.L. 2025 (57 O.S. Supp.
2025, Section 138), which relates to earned credits
18 for inmates; prohibiting certain inmates from
receiving earned credits; and declaring an emergency.
